    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We surfed just above tubes and it was cooking. Easily double overhead, running all the way to point on a good one. I surfed the Custard Queen and just went fast and straight. I pulled into a couple of barrels but didn’t make any. I’m considering putting twin keels into the board to see how it goes? ",
            "link": null
          },
